channel.title: The Sliabs Client
channel.description:
Hello Everyone, unfortunately I'm currently having trouble with The Silab's Client. After I downloaded it and extracted "version 3", "Client" and "Run" popped up on my desktop. I double clicked "Client" and nothing came up. I double clicked "Run" and this came up telling me that I have a problem.
[URL=http://img410.imageshack.us/my.php?image=helpvf4.png][IMG]http://img410.imageshack.us/img410/3130/helpvf4.th.png[/img][/URL]
After seeing this image, you are probably thinking that I have not downloaded Jdk, Well, I have downloaded Jdk, but do I need this many?
[URL=http://img408.imageshack.us/my.php?image=help2ai1.png][IMG]http://img408.imageshack.us/img408/930/help2ai1.th.png[/img][/URL]
I hope you can figure out the problem I am facing.
*Also, if I am posting this in the wrong section please forgive me.
Yours Truly,
